trans-unit.source: Contains a collection of <see cref="T:System.Configuration.PropertyInformation" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: Contém uma coleção de objetos <see cref="T:System.Configuration.PropertyInformation" /> .

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Configuration.PropertyInformationCollection> object contains a collection of <xref:System.Configuration.PropertyInformation> objects.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Configuration.PropertyInformationCollection> objeto contém uma coleção de <xref:System.Configuration.PropertyInformation> objetos.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Configuration.PropertyInformation> object contains the details of an individual attribute within the configuration.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.Configuration.PropertyInformation> objeto contém os detalhes de um atributo individual dentro da configuração.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Configuration.PropertyInformationCollection> object is derived from the associated <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.NameObjectCollectionBase> object.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Configuration.PropertyInformationCollection> objeto é derivado do associado <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.NameObjectCollectionBase> objeto.

trans-unit.source: The following code example demonstrates how to use the <xref:System.Configuration.PropertyInformationCollection> class.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo de código a seguir demonstra como usar o <xref:System.Configuration.PropertyInformationCollection> classe.

trans-unit.source: A one-dimensional <see cref="T:System.Array" /> that is the destination of the elements copied from the <see cref="T:System.Configuration.PropertyInformationCollection" /> collection.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Array" /> unidimensional que é o destino dos elementos copiados da coleção <see cref="T:System.Configuration.PropertyInformationCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Array" /> must have zero-based indexing.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Array" /> deve ter indexação com base em zero.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index in <c>array</c> at which copying begins.
trans-unit.target: O índice baseado em zero na <c>array</c> na qual a cópia começa.

trans-unit.source: Copies the entire <see cref="T:System.Configuration.PropertyInformationCollection" /> collection to a compatible one-dimensional <see cref="T:System.Array" />, starting at the specified index of the target array.
trans-unit.target: Copia toda a coleção <see cref="T:System.Configuration.PropertyInformationCollection" /> para um <see cref="T:System.Array" /> unidimensional compatível, começando no índice especificado da matriz de destino.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="array" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="array" /> é <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.Array.Length" /> property of <paramref name="array" /> is less than <see cref="P:System.Collections.Specialized.NameObjectCollectionBase.Count" /> + <paramref name="index" />.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.Array.Length" /> de <paramref name="array" /> é menor que <see cref="P:System.Collections.Specialized.NameObjectCollectionBase.Count" /> + <paramref name="index" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets an <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" /> object, which is used to iterate through this <see cref="T:System.Configuration.PropertyInformationCollection" /> collection.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um objeto <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" />, que é usado para iterar por esta coleção <see cref="T:System.Configuration.PropertyInformationCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" /> object, which is used to iterate through this <see cref="T:System.Configuration.PropertyInformationCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" />, que é usado para iterar por este <see cref="T:System.Configuration.PropertyInformationCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo" /> object that contains the information required to serialize the <see cref="T:System.Configuration.PropertyInformationCollection" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo" /> que contém as informações necessárias para serializar a instância <see cref="T:System.Configuration.PropertyInformationCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext" /> object that contains the source and destination of the serialized stream associated with the <see cref="T:System.Configuration.PropertyInformationCollection" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext" /> que contém a origem e o destino do fluxo serializado associado à instância <see cref="T:System.Configuration.PropertyInformationCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Populates a <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo" /> object with the data needed to serialize the <see cref="T:System.Configuration.PropertyInformationCollection" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: Preenche um objeto <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo" /> com os dados necessários para serializar a instância <see cref="T:System.Configuration.PropertyInformationCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="info" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="info" /> é <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: The name of the configuration attribute contained in the <see cref="T:System.Configuration.PropertyInformationCollection" />
trans-unit.target: O nome do atributo de configuração contido no <see cref="T:System.Configuration.PropertyInformationCollection" />

trans-unit.source: object.
Gets the <see cref="T:System.Configuration.PropertyInformation" /> object in the collection, based on the specified property name.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o objeto <see cref="T:System.Configuration.PropertyInformation" /> na coleção com base no nome da propriedade especificada.
